jaskell.parsec

类 Between<E,T,O,C,Status,Tran>

  • java.lang.Object
    • jaskell.parsec.Between<E,T,O,C,Status,Tran>
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Parsec<E,T,Status,Tran>

    public class Between<E,T,O,C,Status,Tran>
extends Object
implements Parsec<E,T,Status,Tran>
    Created by Mars Liu on 2016-01-03. Between 算子等效于 open.then(p).over(close); 若 (open, parser, close) 组合子顺序解析成功,返回 parser 的解析结果. 遵循 Haskell Parsec 的定义,我们将参数顺序设定为 between(open, close, parser),并提供了 curry 化的 In 子类型.
